Determines if the elements of this [`Iterator`] are equal to those of
another with respect to the specified equality function.

# Examples

```
#![feature(iter_order_by)]

let xs = [1, 2, 3, 4];
let ys = [1, 4, 9, 16];

assert!(xs.iter().eq_by(ys, |x, y| x * x == y));
```
